  "detailed_description": "Warzone VR is a cross-platform multiplayer virtual reality shooter. Group up with other players and enter a battlefield where real players take part in a massive struggle for dominance. With dedicated servers to support a smooth and competitive experience, Warzone VR was developed from the ground up with cross-platform in mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/b74ab1c7fef131bec3985412297f2be2.poster.avif?t=1605537649\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/b74ab1c7fef131bec3985412297f2be2.webm?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/b74ab1c7fef131bec3985412297f2be2.mp4?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>NEW: CROSSPLAY</strong><br>Crossplay is now possible with players coming in from the Viveport store. The Oculus store is pending release and will join the servers shortly!<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Progression System<br></li><li> Character Customization<br></li><li> In-game Shop & Load-Out Customization<br></li><li> Positional, Team and Open VOIP options (server global)<br></li><li> Interactive Squad Vehicles<br></li><li> Competitive Play</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/4763762019cd9a64e0ce27775d33b856.poster.avif?t=1605537649\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/4763762019cd9a64e0ce27775d33b856.webm?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/4763762019cd9a64e0ce27775d33b856.mp4?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Warzone VR is a cross-platform multiplayer virtual reality shooter. Group up with other players and enter a battlefield where real players take part in a massive struggle for dominance. With dedicated servers to support a smooth and competitive experience, Warzone VR was developed from the ground up with cross-platform in mind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/b74ab1c7fef131bec3985412297f2be2.poster.avif?t=1605537649\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/b74ab1c7fef131bec3985412297f2be2.webm?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/b74ab1c7fef131bec3985412297f2be2.mp4?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>NEW: CROSSPLAY</strong><br>Crossplay is now possible with players coming in from the Viveport store. The Oculus store is pending release and will join the servers shortly!<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Progression System<br></li><li> Character Customization<br></li><li> In-game Shop & Load-Out Customization<br></li><li> Positional, Team and Open VOIP options (server global)<br></li><li> Interactive Squad Vehicles<br></li><li> Competitive Play</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/4763762019cd9a64e0ce27775d33b856.poster.avif?t=1605537649\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/838820/extras/4763762019cd9a64e0ce27775d33b856.webm?t=1605537649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app